<item>
            <title>[PIG-946] Combiner optimizer does not optimize when limit follow group, foreach</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/PIG-946</link>
                <project id="12310730" key="PIG">Pig</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;The following script is combinable but is not optimized:&lt;br/&gt;
a = load &apos;/user/pig/tests/data/singlefile/studenttab10k&apos;;&lt;br/&gt;
b = group a by $1;&lt;br/&gt;
c = foreach b generate group, AVG(a.$2);&lt;br/&gt;
d = limit c 10;&lt;br/&gt;
dump d;&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment></environment>
        <key id="12434896">PIG-946</key>
            <summary>Combiner optimizer does not optimize when limit follow group, foreach</summary>
